                          <lb n="46"/>ἀξίως ἀμφοτερᾶν τᾶν <rs type="institution" subtype="social_group" role="good_relations_or_behaviour" key="polis" ref="#erannos"><w lemma="πόλις">πολίων</w></rs>, ἦμεν
                          <lb n="47"/>δὲ αὐτὸς καὶ <rs type="institution" subtype="social_status" role="granted_as_privilege" key="proxenos" ref="#erannos"><w lemma="πρόξενος">προξένος</w></rs> τᾶς τῶν <placeName ref="#erannos" type="ethnic">Ἐραν<lb 
